<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_cærdæg" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>cærdæg</orth></form><sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>проворный</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>brisk</q></cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>быстрый</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>quick</q></cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>ловкий</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>nimble</q></cit></sense></sense><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_cærdæg." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>aztæ jyl bīræ cæwy, fælæ nyrma cærdæg ū</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>лет ему много, но пока еще он живой (бодрый)</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>he is many years old, but he is still alive (brisk)</q></cit></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>aztæ jyl bīræ cæwy, fælæ nyrma cærdæg ū</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>лет ему много, но пока еще он живой (бодрый)</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>he is many years old, but he is still alive (brisk)</q></cit></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Собственно „живой“, прош. причастие от <xr><ref target="#entry_cæryn"/></xr> ‘жить’ + суффикс -%iæg%i. Ср. по образованию <xr><ref target="#entry_lystæg"/></xr> ‘мелкий’, <xr><ref target="#entry_syǧdæg"/></xr> ‘чистый’, <xr><ref target="#entry_cadæg"/></xr> ‘тихий’ и др. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>čālāk</w><gloss><q>ловкий</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><gloss><q>проворный</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It is in fact “alive”, a past participle form of the verb <xr><ref target="#entry_cæryn"/></xr> ‘live’ + suffix -%iæg%i. Cf. by the composition <xr><ref target="#entry_lystæg"/></xr> ‘small’, <xr><ref target="#entry_syǧdæg"/></xr> ‘clean’, <xr><ref target="#entry_cadæg"/></xr> ‘quiet’ etc. Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>čālāk</w><gloss><q>nimble</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><gloss><q>brisk</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym></entry>